<br>
And I tried to keep some of the names very simple. Keiko is a real easy name to remember because it's common. Mamoru is also common, and it means &quot;protect&quot;. Iaka is actually a character of mine on EverQuest, which is Akai spelled backwards (Akai means &quot;Red&quot;.) Shosetsu might be the most difficult name to remember, but you can't just have a ton of plain names. The Dairyoku and the Daimamori are reasy to remember. Mamori means Defense, Guard, etc. and sounds similar to Mamoru (the guy who wields it.) and Ryoku means Power, Strength, etc. (the Dai, means Big, Great, etc.)<br>
I found the same problems when I read Tolkien's &quot;Lord of the Rings&quot; epic. I could only remember Frodo and Gandalf, other than those two, I can't remember the rest of the people in the story.<br>
Maybe I should make it easier on the brain because this will be targeting american audiences.<br>
<br>
I have another name I'll probably use somewhere in there.<br>
<br>
Natsumi= a female character (fairly common name.) For some reason she tags along with Mamoru and Keiko.<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.kabalarians.com/female/natsumi.htm">www.kabalarians.com/female/natsumi.htm</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
<br>
I won't go into detail on who the poet/poetess , because everything that describes him/her in the beginning and en will be in soliloquy-clad poems. and everything in the middle just regular short-verse poetry. I'll let the reader decide who the heck they think the poet/poetess could be. Hell, Maybe Shosetsu will live, and he'll be writing about it (his name can be translated into a few things, one of them is &quot;novel&quot;) It might be Keiko, or Mamoru. I'll just let the reader speculate, now that I took out the idea that the poet/poetess is the writer of a book(set of poems) which is the story. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kagebu>Kagebu</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0> at: 1/2/03 9:32:40 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=durakken>Durakken</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Fresh Meat</span><br> <font color=#336699>(1/2/03 10:15:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=881.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Idea... Whatcha think?</span><hr size=1> PSOJ with his real name mwaff -<br>
