   I'm sure your names'll be fine, but seriously you need to know who you're writing your manga for. I'd imagine it's for your adverage western manga fan, fans of blade of the immortal and soforth. In that case perhaps having a bishonen leading character may not be such a good idea...etc..etc... <br>
   I guess i'm just trying to give advice as to how strongly your audience should direct your plotline if you want a successful comic. I understand you're probably writing it for yourself, but you represent a portion of the populace too.<br>
Good Luck anyway.<br>
